  "wave_0_per_point": "n = t1;\ngmegabuf (n) = (value1 + value2) * 0.4/(sample+0.01);\n\nx = sample;\ny = 0.5 - gmegabuf(5000+n)*0.1;\nt1 += 1;",
  "wave_1_per_frame": "t1 = 0;",
  "wave_1_per_point": "dis = reg00;\nn = t1;\nx = int(n/dis) *dis/512/2*1 /2 + 0.497;\n\ny0 = gmegabuf (5000+n/dis) * (n%dis < 2);\n\ny = y0*0.01;\nt1 += 1;\n\na = !(n%dis<=0) && !(n%dis>=dis);\ny += 0.5 + (y-0.5)*q31;",
  "wave_2_per_frame": "t1 = 0;",
  "wave_2_per_point": "dis = reg00;\nn = t1;\nx = int(n/dis) *dis/512/2*1 /2 +0.746;\n\ny0 = gmegabuf (5000+n/dis+128) * (n%dis < 2) ;\n\ny = y0*0.01;\nt1 += 1;\n\na = !(n%dis<=0) && !(n%dis>=dis);\ny += 0.5+ (y-0.5)*q31;",
  "shape_1_per_frame": "n = (instance);\nFLen = reg00;\nSLen = reg00/2;\n\nz0 = 10;\ny0 = gmegabuf(2000+n+FLen)/z0;\nx0 = gmegabuf(2000+n)/z0;\n\na0 = (gmegabuf(n+10000));\n\nk1 = instance/num_inst-.5;\nx = .5 + x0 + sin(k1*8*sin(q12*.07)) * sin(q11*.13)*q3*.7;\ny = .5 + q32*(y0 + sin(k1*8*sin(q14*.1)) * sin(q13*.2)*q3*.7);\n\narg = q2/8;\nhigh = exp(-500*pow(arg+.5-instance/num_inst,2));\nhigh += exp(-500*pow(-arg+.5-instance/num_inst,2));\n\nexc = sqrt((pow(x-.5,2)+pow(y-.5,2)));\nrad0 = above(z0,0)*min (.1, a0/60)+.005;\nrad0 = rad0 * (1+2*exc) * (1+high);\n\np1 = .5 + sin(q12)/2;\np2 = .5 + sin(q13*1.4)/2;\n//p1 = rand(1)-.5;\n//p2 = rand(1)-.5;\nexc = ((pow(x-p1,2)+pow(y-p2,2)));\nrad = min(rad0 * (1 + .004*q3/abs(exc)),1) ;\n\na = min(a0*8+.4,1);\n\nk1 = instance/num_inst*5 + high;\nw = 1-exp(-treb_att/2-.5);\ng = w + (1-w)*sin(k1);\nr = w + (1-w)*sin(k1-6.28/3);\nb = w + (1-w)*sin(k1-6.28*2/3);\n\na2 = a/4;\ng2 = g*0; b2 = b*0; r2 = r*0;",
  "shape_2_per_frame": "k1 = instance/num_inst;\nx = .5 + .3*sin(instance*k1*413);\ny = .5 + .3 * sin(instance*k1*113);\n\nrad = .1 + .4*sin(k1*333);\n\nr =  .5*sin(k1*234);\nb =  .5*sin(k1*534);\ng =  .5*sin(k1*34);"
